{"tid":2008541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"講下點解國歌法咁重要，建制咁重視，以及澳門咁聽話","createTime":"2020-05-09T06:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T10:46:06.000Z","uid":149978,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1700d919f381a7d5f5c0e4af816efc03736571bd","tid":2008541,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:11:00.000Z","msg":"國歌法立法原因：<br />\n歷史：因為香港球迷噓國歌<br />\n表象：中共玻璃心<br />\n實際：中共要同香港人講，一國兩制，一國比兩制大。基本法，中共全部話晒事。中央給予香港有幾多權力，香港就有幾多權力（參考2014年一國兩制白皮書）<br />\n<br />\n香港人理解：一國 &lt; 兩制<br />\n中央政府：一國 &gt; 兩制<br />\n<br />\n點解澳門咁聽話，但香港又咁頑劣要反抗？<br />\n簡單來說，澳門係旅遊城市，香港係國際金融城市。9成旅客都來自中國，如果中央收回自由行，澳門經濟基本玩完，但對香港經濟影響唔到百分之十。說白點，澳門沒有反抗的本錢，香港仲有。"},{"pid":"3dbf6a2a28b10168fe59a5c4bb29eedf206b72b2","tid":2008541,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"510 一齊出尖沙咀反對班狗嘅反對通知書！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2008512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2008512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe9311d6e8bcddd39ed82ab49dfaf88f265278d5","tid":2008541,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"如果中國沒有香港，對中國經濟和民生都係打擊。<br />\n<br />\n如果中國沒有澳門，對中國經濟和民生反而利多於弊。因為澳門只是一個賭城，基本上可有可無。其實無左澳門，中國人無咁易走去賭，中國會更好。"},{"pid":"d214da1895ace5ba84e50517e3be380273a7e5f8","tid":2008541,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404cd2daae003a737d63097b07cbc352cb53878c","tid":2008541,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:37:12.000Z","msg":"國歌法，就係中央要同香港人講，一國兩制，一國比兩制大。"},{"pid":"03f75326f3388ef4d653b6a910d0b5f6cac4fe48","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"澳門咁聽話其中一個原因係葡萄牙廢"},{"pid":"8b094bc6fff6d8406b094875c2575fc90f0ca011","tid":2008541,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03f75326f3388ef4d653b6a910d0b5f6cac4fe48","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"澳門咁聽話其中一個原因係葡萄牙廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"英國唔廢?"},{"pid":"1175f957cb053ebe2c71c649be8835f104e042ae","tid":2008541,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n賀一誠開到口要開關要大陸遊客去拯救經濟<br />\n澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fea4ff4a9cc7193174afbea38c01191257b410","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b094bc6fff6d8406b094875c2575fc90f0ca011","tid":2008541,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03f75326f3388ef4d653b6a910d0b5f6cac4fe48","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"澳門咁聽話其中一個原因係葡萄牙廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"英國唔廢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"英殖管治好過葡殖十倍"},{"pid":"78596b4b08f60c7fff6197a2a72772b1cb9696a1","tid":2008541,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03f75326f3388ef4d653b6a910d0b5f6cac4fe48","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"澳門咁聽話其中一個原因係葡萄牙廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"其實澳門嘅 一二三 事件都係令澳門係主權移交前變得親中國嘅原因之一"},{"pid":"4b1253728807fd78b029aafcd9162abbb6b7f42d","tid":2008541,"uid":203185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78596b4b08f60c7fff6197a2a72772b1cb9696a1","tid":2008541,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03f75326f3388ef4d653b6a910d0b5f6cac4fe48","tid":2008541,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"澳門咁聽話其中一個原因係葡萄牙廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"其實澳門嘅 一二三 事件都係令澳門係主權移交前變得親中國嘅原因之一"